CC  Bacimethrin is a natural product made from CMP. It is a thiamin analog,
CC  a toxic antivitamin made as an antibiotic. The pathway order is
CC  hydroxymethylation by BcmA, N-glycosyl bond cleavage by BcmB,
CC  SAM-dependent methylation by BcmC, pyrophosphorylation by BcmD.
